This crawler is designed to crawl news articles. Fetching articles for a given year is easy as typing

  python blogSearch.py query start_year [start_month] [window size]

for example
  python blogSearch.py "Northern Gateway Pipeline" 2012 01 3

fetches all articles about the northern gateway pipeline in 2012, starting from January with 3 month rolling windows.

start_month and window_size are optional parameters that default to 01 and 3 respectively.

The output is organized in the results directory. also a cache of websearches is kept and may need to be manually deleted due to space restrictions.

Dependencies:
   BeautifulSoup
   pycurl
